content:
Manage Prediction Definitions

Use the Model Manager to manage prediction definitions in your org.

View a Prediction Definition: Manage a prediction definition and its associated models.
Configure Automatic Model Refresh for a Prediction Definition: Schedule regular, unattended model updates on a weekly or monthly basis.
Configure Automated Prediction Writeback for a Prediction Definition: Save numeric prediction scores to a field in a Salesforce object using automated writeback.
Configure Performance Monitoring for a Prediction Definition: Configure performance monitoring charts for a prediction definition and receive notifications if performance falls below thresholds.
Configure Model Quality Notifications: Set alert thresholds, schedule performance evaluation cycles, and specify who will receive notifications.
Configure the Model Card for a Prediction Definition: Document important usage information about your predictions with model cards.
Analyze Prediction Accuracy with the Einstein Accuracy Analytics App: Monitor how well your models predict actual outcomes over time.
title: Managing Prediction Definitions in Salesforce
